# --- Project Specific ---
# Simulation Outputs (don't track generated plots in root-ish dirs)
# Keep them in specific output folders if needed, or track them if they are assets.
# But generally avoid tracking temporary simulation results.
*.png
*.svg
*.pdf

# Exception for documentation assets (if you want to strictly track doc images)
!docs/assets/*.png
!docs/assets/*.svg

# Sandbox - Experiments
sandbox/*
!sandbox/README.md
!sandbox/legacy_circuit_model_analysis/

